BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 580 Td (Not everyone will want to be your friend, and that's OKAY. Rejection hurts,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 562 Td (but it doesn't mean there's something wrong with you. It means that person) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 544 Td (isn't your match. There are 8 billion people on Earth - you only need a few) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 526 Td (good friends! When rejected, don't beg or change yourself. Thank them) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 508 Td (politely, feel your feelings, and move on to find YOUR people.) Tj ET

