BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 214.8 670 Td (Resolving Conflicts) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 580 Td (Even best friends fight sometimes! Conflict doesn't mean the friendship is) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 562 Td (over - it means you care enough to be honest. Healthy conflict resolution:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 544 Td (1\) Cool down before talking. 2\) Use 'I feel' statements \(not 'You) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 526 Td (always...'\). 3\) Listen to their side. 4\) Find a compromise. 5\) Apologize) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 508 Td (for your part. 6\) Forgive and move forward.) Tj ET

