BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 210.0 670 Td (Dealing with Bullies) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 580 Td (Bullying is NOT normal conflict - it's repeated, intentional harm. If) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 562 Td (someone consistently hurts you physically, verbally, or socially, that's) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 544 Td (bullying. You should: 1\) Tell a trusted adult. 2\) Don't fight back \(it) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 526 Td (escalates\). 3\) Stay with friends \(safety in numbers\). 4\) Document what) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 508 Td (happens. 5\) Know it's NOT your fault. You deserve to be safe.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
