BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 526 Td (respected, supported, and free to be yourself. You deserve healthy) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 508 Td (friendships. It's okay to walk away from toxic ones.) Tj ET

